  "rationale": "An hourglass of a human life. The top bulb is densely packed with white dots (decades lived); the bottom is sparse (the end is short). One RED grain of sand sits in the bottom — the final moment. The neck pinches in the middle where the seconds pass. 320px mixed-case 'Being / Mortal' title in weight 300, centered. The visual thesis: life is mostly behind us, and the bottom of the hourglass is the only part the book is about."
